criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Singleton pregnancy between 14 and 20 weeks gestation;

          -  Literate women;

          -  sedentary lifestyle.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cognitive, auditory, visual or motor impairment, certified by a specialist;

          -  Any pregnancy disorders or previous maternal diseases: diabetes type 1 or type 2,
             hypertensive disorders of pregnancy, hemodynamic instability, renal disease or
             collagen, vaginal bleeding;

          -  Any medical or obstetric contraindication to perform physical activity.
